{"tid":363932,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS 11允許用戶必要時快速禁用Touch ID","createTime":"2017-08-18T03:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T15:43:14.000Z","uid":1193,"like":403,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bec738deca43f6b5af2f2849fd49414248e74845","tid":363932,"uid":1193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"根據 The Verge 的消息，蘋果推出了一個新功能，可以讓 iPhone 用戶快速禁用 Touch ID。如果你遇到某些會迫使你解鎖 iPhone 的情況，這個功能可能會派上用場。在最新的 iOS 11 公共測試版中，你可以快速按下電源按鍵 5 次來獲取緊急呼叫服務或者禁用 Touch ID。<br />\n<br />\n完成這個操作之後，你的 iPhone 會為你提供緊急呼叫服務，同時還會在你的 iPhone 上禁用 Touch ID，並迫使你輸入密碼以再次啟用這項指紋識別功能。如果你想在 iPhone 上快速禁用 Touch ID 的話，這是一個非常有用的功能。在此之前，iPhone 禁用 Touch ID 的唯一方法就是重啟設備，而在緊急情況下，快速按 5 次電源鍵要更方便。<br />\n<br />\n生於亂世 有種電話叫iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc343c16fee05bd446b8d1c00e09cfd414641517","tid":363932,"uid":16453,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"俾狗拉之前activate 咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf54138db2288139032e9c1ae63ff5a949d8d67c","tid":363932,"uid":81113,"like":89,"dislike":7,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:04:48.000Z","msg":"勁！咁都比蘋果諗到！<br />\n留名睇android跟風"},{"pid":"b89ae14c8c6f336b6718bd3a47a5d6291aea2744","tid":363932,"uid":36551,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"香港人必備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea52c78fa167dcaf44037249d06763baeaec5c3","tid":363932,"uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418fedc2315e9e738361f3e2fe0bcf4cc19ed8c1","tid":363932,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201