唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你咪可以自己決定講定唔講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你覺得資料好機密影響未來既 你又有勇氣做烈士咪死都唔講囉<br />\n但你隻手指比人捉住擺係粒掣到 有冇得控制解唔解鎖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 用腦係咪咁撚辛苦你"},{"pid":"76e4976a2785a476d2e352450a426f46fcde675e","tid":363932,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"正 如果3下啟用就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先試下連按5野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好唔就手既感覺"},{"pid":"0c985447ab3ba14a2e2d7e2e334cb7b52d8e08bd","tid":363932,"uid":25050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"一開頭就唔用Touch ID 直接用密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79605b8db8898852b00d0a4dae2b6101be1ddc8","tid":363932,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁如果比人迫入密碼呢？唔迫你用touchid咪迫你入密碼囉 有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n走啦 屌你老母弱智仔</blockquote><br />\n唉，連登淪落到呢件弱智垃圾都有ac, 比人笑小學雞論壇真係低撚死"}]}